    <link xlink:href="pubmed:9012496"/>
    <link xlink:href="pubmed:9814706"/>
  </linklist>
  <comment>Pnt activates Aos in the neuroectoderm (Chang et al., 2003).

Overexpression of pntP1 may reduce expression of EGFR targets rhomboid and 69D (unpublished data mentionned by Morimoto, et al., 1996)

Pnt may activate Argos in the FCE (unpublished data mentionned by Wasserman and Freeman, 1998).</comment>
</annotation>
